            <note xml:id="foot.f2">Hooker’s letter has not been found.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">CD had written to Hooker to request specimens of the orchid <hi rend="italic">Bonatea</hi> (see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-3315.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to J. D. Hooker, 10 November [1861]</ref>).</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-3315.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to J. D. Hooker, 10 November [1861]</ref>, n. 3 and the diagram.</note>
